# Main Page Loop (Strict)

Use for `/`, `/about/`, `/services/`, `/blog/`, `/categories/`, `/tags/`, `/contact/` only.

1. Create `temp_main_pages_checklist.txt` with seven paths (one per line, `- [ ] /path/`).
2. Edit hero copy only in `src/lib/seo/main-page-heroes.mjs` (SSOT).
3. Align `export const metadata` in matching `src/app/**/page.tsx` (title, description 120–165 chars, keyword).
4. Deepen TSX body copy under `MainPageHero` where needed; use trailing slashes on internal `Link href`.
5. Run `pnpm run seo:guardrails`.
6. Run `pnpm build`.
7. Mark path `[x]` in checklist.

Hard requirements:
- Intro 130–200 Hebrew words; include a `SITE_KEYWORDS` phrase; no style-meta blocklist phrases.
- Brand: prefer `גיא אבני` / `גיא אבני עו״ד` / `גיא אבני עורך דין` on heroes.
- Do not edit `src/content/blog/*.mdx`.
- Log: `[main-page-loop] step N` or `ERROR`.
